{"type":"message","id":"9f466c2b","parentId":"34c96f4f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T08:46:16.179Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了，我找到了 openclaw.json 文件，里面有所有 providers 的详细信息。让我整理一下这些数据，以清晰的格式呈现给小王子。\n\n从配置中我可以看到：\n\n1. **custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com** (阿里云 DashScope):\n   - 模型：qwen3.5-plus\n   - input: [\"text\"]\n   - cost: input: 0, output: 0, cacheRead: 0, cacheWrite: 0 (免费)\n   - contextWindow: 16000\n   - maxTokens: 4096\n\n2. **minimax**:\n   - 模型：MiniMax-M2.5\n   - input: [\"text\"]\n   - cost: input: 0.3, output: 1.2, cacheRead: 0.03, cacheWrite: 0.12 (美元/百万 tokens)\n   - contextWindow: 200000\n   - maxTokens: 8192\n   - reasoning: true\n\n3. **moonshot** (Kimi):\n   - 模型：kimi-k2.5\n   - input: [\"text\", \"image\"]\n   - cost: input: 0, output: 0, cacheRead: 0, cacheWrite: 0 (免费)\n   - contextWindow: 256000\n   - maxTokens: 8192\n\n还有 openrouter 的配置在 auth.profiles 中提到，但模型详情没有在这个文件里。\n\n让我用清晰的表格格式呈现这些信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"小王子，这是你配置的模型提供商详情：\n\n| 提供商 | 模型 | Input 类型 | 价格 (USD/MT) | Context Window | Max Tokens |\n|--------|------|-----------|--------------|----------------|------------|\n| **阿里云 DashScope** | qwen3.5-plus | text | 免费 | 16,000 | 4,096 |\n| **MiniMax** | MiniMax-M2.5 | text | 输入 $0.3 / 输出 $1.2 | 200,000 | 8,192 |\n| **Moonshot (Kimi)** | kimi-k2.5 | text + image | 免费 | 256,000 | 8,192 |\n| **OpenRouter** | auto (动态) | - | 按实际模型计费 | - | - |\n\n**当前默认模型**：`custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com/qwen3.5-plus`\n\n**备注**：\n- MiniMax 支持 reasoning 模式\n- Kimi 支持图像输入\n- OpenRouter 是聚合平台，实际价格取决于路由到的具体模型\n\n需要我帮你调整默认模型或添加更多模型吗？🦊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773996363320}}
