{"type":"message","id":"66f8c51e","parentId":"38fc9a69","timestamp":"2026-03-20T08:48:17.032Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经更新了 models.json 文件。现在让我向用户汇报更新结果。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"小王子，我已经更新了 `models.json` 配置文件：\n\n**更新后的价格**：\n\n| 提供商 | 模型 | Input ($/M) | Output ($/M) | Context | Max Tokens |\n|--------|------|-------------|--------------|---------|------------|\n| **阿里云** | Qwen3.5-Plus | $0.60 (¥4.5) | $2.80 (¥20) | 32K | 8K |\n| **MiniMax** | M2.5 | $0.30 (¥2) | $1.20 (¥8) | 200K | 8K |\n| **Moonshot** | Kimi K2.5 | $1.70 (¥12) | $8.50 (¥60) | 256K | 8K |\n| **OpenRouter** | Auto | 动态 | 动态 | 200K | 8K |\n\n**备注**：\n- OpenRouter 是聚合平台，实际价格取决于路由到的具体模型（有免费模型如 DeepSeek R1、Llama 3 等）\n- MiniMax 价格相对最便宜，适合长上下文任务\n- Kimi K2.5 最贵但支持 256K 上下文和图像输入\n- Qwen3.5-Plus 性价比不错，适合日常任务\n\n配置文件已保存，下次会话会使用新价格计算成本。🦊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773996490386}}
