{"type":"message","id":"8e4eedbd","parentId":"e5c5fef3","timestamp":"2026-03-20T08:53:35.243Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已成功更新 Kimi K2.5 的配置，现在需要向用户总结更新后的参数，并提供所有模型的完整对比表格。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"小王子，已更新 Moonshot Kimi K2.5 的配置！\n\n**Kimi K2.5 修正后参数**：\n\n| 参数 | 之前（错误） | 现在（正确） |\n|------|-------------|-------------|\n| **Context Window** | 256K | **262K** (256K) |\n| **Max Tokens** | 8K | **65K** |\n| **Input** | $1.70/M | **$0.45/M** (OpenRouter) |\n| **Output** | $8.50/M | **$2.20/M** (OpenRouter) |\n| **Cache Read** | 0 | **$0.05/M** |\n| **Cache Write** | 0 | **$0.10/M** |\n| **Reasoning** | false | **true** (支持思考模式) |\n| **多模态** | ✅ | ✅ (text + image) |\n\n**价格说明**：\n- OpenRouter 价格：$0.45/M 输入，$2.20/M 输出\n- 官网 API 价格：约 $0.60/M 输入，$2.50/M 输出\n- 缓存命中时享有折扣\n\n**完整模型对比**（更新后）：\n\n| 模型 | Input ($/M) | Output ($/M) | Context | Max Tokens | Reasoning |\n|------|-------------|--------------|---------|------------|-----------|\n| Qwen3.5-Plus | $0.11 | $0.28 | 256K | 16K | ✅ |\n| MiniMax M2.5 | $0.30 | $1.20 | 200K | 8K | ✅ |\n| Kimi K2.5 | $0.45 | $2.20 | 256K | 65K | ✅ |\n| OpenRouter Auto | 动态 | 动态 | 200K | 8K | 动态 |\n\n现在所有价格都是真实的了！🦊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773996805804}}
